---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Your Guide - Matt O'Leary | Walk Santa Cruz"
	description="Meet Matt O'Leary, your local Santa Cruz guide. A native with a passion for sharing the rich history and vibrant culture of our coastal community."
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="full-bleed bg-accent/20 py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Your Guide</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
					Local expertise, passionate storytelling
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- About Content -->
	<section class="container py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Guide photo placeholder -->
			<div class="mb-12">
				<div class="aspect-[3/2] max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
					<p class="text-muted-foreground">Matt O'Leary - Photo Coming Soon</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
					Hi! I'm <strong>Matt O'Leary</strong>, and I grew up in Santa Cruz, where I went to Santa Cruz High and UC Santa Cruz. I've spent countless hours exploring the beaches, redwoods, and neighborhoods that make this area so special — and I love helping others experience it too.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
					When I'm not leading tours, I work as a designer and web developer, and I've also taught surfing lessons — both casually and professionally. I enjoy spending time outdoors with my wife and kids, whether it's hiking local trails or catching waves. That same spirit of sharing what I love inspired me to start Walk Santa Cruz.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
					What began as casual walks with friends has grown into a way to help visitors and locals alike see Santa Cruz through a new lens — discovering the hidden gems this town and its surrounding beaches and mountains have to offer.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
					I believe the best way to experience this place is on foot — it's a healthy, fun way to slow down, take in the scenery, and connect with the stories that make Santa Cruz unique.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8">
					I look forward to walking with you soon!
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- CTA -->
			<div class="text-center mt-12">
				<button data-booking-modal class="btn btn-lg">Book a Tour</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Why Walk With Us -->
	<section class="full-bleed bg-accent/20 py-16 md:py-24">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Why Walk With Us</h2>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<div class="card">
						<div class="p-6">
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Local Expertise</h3>
							<p class="text-muted-foreground">Our guides are Santa Cruz natives with deep knowledge and passion for our community's history and culture.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="card">
						<div class="p-6">
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Small Groups</h3>
							<p class="text-muted-foreground">Enjoy personalized attention with our small group sizes or opt for a private tour experience.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="card">
						<div class="p-6">
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Hidden Gems</h3>
							<p class="text-muted-foreground">Discover secret spots and fascinating stories that even locals might not know about.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="card">
						<div class="p-6">
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Easy & Accessible</h3>
							<p class="text-muted-foreground">Our tours are designed to be comfortable for most fitness levels with plenty of stops along the way.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
